England, Sri Lanka Take Early Lunch as Rain Again Hits First Cricket Test

-- B y   P e t e r - J o s e p h   H e g a r t y
-- 
2011-05-29T12:06:38Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-29/england-sri-lanka-take-early-lunch-as-rain-again-hits-first-cricket-test.html
England  and  Sri Lanka  players took an
early lunch as rain again disrupted play in the first cricket
Test at Cardiff.  Sri Lanka reached 400 all out in its first innings.
Alastair Cook is 129 not out and  Jonathan Trott  is on 125 after
England reached 287-2 on another rain-shortened third day
yesterday.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Peter-Joseph Hegarty at 
 phegarty@bloomberg.net  